The unique name of the cluster for which snapshots should be listed.

Values are of the form projects/<project>/instances/<instance>/clusters/<cluster>. Use <cluster> = '-' to list snapshots for all clusters in an instance, e.g., projects/<project>/instances/<instance>/clusters/-.
